        "Check 3 Variable with mismatching sorts or capitalization",
        "Check 4 Reserved names (position-dependent set: {K,KU,KD} on LHS/RHS, +{In,Out,Fr} in actions)",
        "Check 5 Fr facts must only use a fresh- or a msg-variable",
